<h2 style="padding-top: 0;text-align:center"><a name="1" id="1"></a>The TechCrunch visual explorer by Infomous</h2>
<p>
The TechCrunch visual explorer is based on the <strong><a
href="http://www.infomous.com" target="_blank">Infomous</a></strong>
interactive text cloud technology. This cloud is collecting information from relevant sections of TechCrunch to help users find more content related to the article or page they just visited.</p>

<p>Word size indicates how often that word occurs in the articles. Related terms and concepts are linked together with lines.</p>

<p>Click a word to show a list of links to relevant stories on TechCrunch. Click
any link to open that article in a new page. </p>

<p>Find out more at <a href="http://get.infomous.com">the Infomous web
site</a></p>

